---
import {
  AlertTriangle,
  ArrowLeft,
  ChevronDown,
  ChevronRight,
  CircleHelp,
  Code2,
  MessageCircle,
  Moon,
  Search,
  Send,
  Sun,
  X
} from "@lucide/astro";
import "../styles/site.css";

interface Props {
  title: string;
  description?: string;
  page: "home" | "about" | "fonts" | "font" | "login" | "dashboard" | "notFound";
}

const { title, description = "免費中文字體 Webfont 服務", page } = Astro.props;
const apiBase = (import.meta.env.PUBLIC_EMFONT_API_BASE ?? "").replace(/\/$/, "");
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-Hant" data-api-base={apiBase}>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta name="author" content="毛哥EM" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="emfont, webfont, 中文字體, 開源" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0f172a" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="emfont" />
    <meta property="og:locale" content="zh-TW" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/assets/img/og.webp" />
    <meta property="og:image:alt" content="emfont - 免費中文字體 Webfont 服務" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/img/logo/favicon-96x96.png" sizes="96x96" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/assets/img/logo/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/assets/img/logo/favicon.ico" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/assets/img/logo/apple-touch-icon.png" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="emfont" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="/assets/img/logo/site.webmanifest" />
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-H69XEEC798"></script>
    <script is:inline>
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      function gtag() {
        dataLayer.push(arguments);
      }
      gtag("js", new Date());
      gtag("config", "G-H69XEEC798");
    </script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">跳到主要內容</a>
    <main id="main-content" class={page} role="main">
      <input type="checkbox" name="lightmode" id="lightmode" />
      <input type="checkbox" id="mobileToggle" />
      <section>
        <div id="section-about">
          <p>
            emfont 是一款免費、簡單易用的 CJK webfont（網頁中文字體）服務，讓你只需在網站內加上兩行 JavaScript，並在元素上套用 class，就能立即套用豐富的字型。不論是形象網站、作品集，還是部落格，都能大幅提升視覺質感。
          </p>
          <p>目前 emfont 提供超過 90 款開源中文字型。輕巧，穩定，不必處理繁瑣的設定，也不需擔心版權問題，讓設計和開發專注於創意本身。</p>
          <p>
            本專案特別感謝 <a href="https://zeabur.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zeabur</a> 及 <a href="https://sponsor.ncse.tw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">國雲網路</a> 提供台灣高速穩定的運算資源。讓 emfont 能持續為大家提供優質服務。而最重要的，是每一位使用者的支持。
          </p>
          <p>
            如果你喜歡這個開源專案，歡迎在 <a href="https://github.com/emfont/emfont">GitHub</a> 留下一顆星星，或 <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/elvismao">用實際行動</a> 來支援 emfont。而如果你有任何問題或有興趣協助開發，不要吝嗇在我們的 <a href="https://dc.elvismao.com">Discord 伺服器</a> 中提出。
          </p>
          <div class="credits">
            <div class="contributors">
              <h2>貢獻者</h2>
              <div>
                <a href="https://elvismao.com" class="contributor">
                  <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/61068739" alt="毛哥EM" loading="lazy" />
                  毛哥EM
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/iach526526" class="contributor">
                  <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/98824625" alt="Each Chan" loading="lazy" />
                  Each Chan
                </a>
                <a href="https://pan93.com" class="contributor">
                  <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/28441561" alt="Yi-Jyun Pan" loading="lazy" />
                  Yi-Jyun Pan
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sponsors">
              <h2>贊助</h2>
              <div>
                <a href="https://zeabur.com/?referralCode=Edit-Mr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Zeabur">
                  <img src="/assets/img/Zeabur.svg" alt="Zeabur" />
                </a>
                <a href="https://sponsor.ncse.tw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  <img src="/assets/img/NCSE.svg" class="ncse" alt="國雲網路 logo" />
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/elvismao" class="buy-me-a-coffee" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <img src="https://img.buymeacoffee.com/button-api/?text=Buy me a Red Bull&emoji=&slug=elvismao&button_colour=FFDD00&font_colour=000000&font_family=Bree&outline_colour=000000&coffee_colour=ffffff" alt="支持 emfont" />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="section-home">
          <div class="emfont-GenYoGothicTC-min"><span>不必微軟正黑可以源樣黑體</span></div>
          <div class="emfont-GenYoMinTC-min"><span>不必新細明體可以源樣明體</span></div>
          <div class="emfont-jfOpenHuninn-min"><span>不必思源黑體可以open粉圓</span></div>
          <div class="emfont-MantouSans-min"><span>不必Roboto可以饅頭黑體</span></div>
          <div class="emfont-ChenYuLuoYan-min"><span>不必蘋果儷中黑可以辰宇落雁體</span></div>
          <div class="emfont-ChillBitmap16px-min"><span>不必標楷體可以寒蝉点阵体</span></div>
        </div>

        <div id="section-404">
          <div>
            <h1>404</h1>
            <h2>找不到這個頁面</h2>
            <p>
              Hold on, if love is the answer, you're <a href="/">home</a>.<br />
              - Daft Punk, Touch<br />
              <a href="/">回到首頁</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="section-login">
          <div>
            <h1>登入</h1>
            <p>查看你的網頁的統計資料</p>
            <a href="/login/github" class="btn">
              <Code2 aria-hidden="true" />
              透過 GitHub 繼續
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="section-search"></div>
        <div id="section-font">
          <div class="section-font-container">
            <div class="font-weights"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="first-time">
              <h2>第一次使用 emfont？</h2>
              <p>
                emfont 是一個免費的網頁字體 (Webfont) 服務，會自動壓縮與最佳化字型檔案。你可以 <a href="/docs/setup">閱讀文檔來快速入門</a>。
              </p>
            </div>
            <footer role="contentinfo">
              <img src="/assets/img/logo/emfont-icon-gray.svg" alt="emfont 標誌" class="footer-logo" />
              <p>
                文字是網站的靈魂，是思想的表達，更是美感的載體。然而中文字體因為檔案龐大、需要耗費大量流量，很少有免費中文字體的 webfont 服務。emfont 的誕生正是為了填補這一空白，整理了許多開源免費的字體。
              </p>
              <a href="https://zeabur.com/?referralCode=Edit-Mr" class="footer-zeabur">
                <img src="/assets/img/Zeabur-deploy.svg" alt="Deployed on Zeabur" />
              </a>
            </footer>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <header role="banner">
        <label class="mobile-nav" for="mobileToggle" aria-label="開啟導覽">
          <ChevronRight aria-hidden="true" />
        </label>
        <a href="/"><img src="/assets/img/logo/emfont-logo-light.svg" id="logo" height="44.8" width="250" alt="emfont 標誌" /></a>
        <div class="header-container">
          <nav class="navigation" aria-label="主導覽">
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/fonts" id="font-button">字型</a></li>
              <li><a href="/docs">文件</a></li>
              <li><a href="/about">關於</a></li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
          <h1>免費的中文 Webfont 服務</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="search-container fontPage-container" role="search" aria-label="字型搜尋">
          <a class="navigation" href="/">
            <ArrowLeft class="icon" aria-hidden="true" />
            字型
          </a>
          <label for="search-input" class="sr-only">搜尋字型</label>
          <div class="search-field">
            <Search class="field-icon" aria-hidden="true" />
            <input type="text" id="search-input" placeholder="搜尋字型" aria-label="搜尋字型" />
          </div>
          <h2>即時測試</h2>
          <label for="search-test" class="sr-only">即時測試文字</label>
          <textarea id="search-test" rows="3" placeholder="我個人認為義大利麵就應該拌42號混泥土。" aria-label="即時測試文字"></textarea>
          <h2>分類</h2>
          <div class="category"></div>
          <h2>家族</h2>
          <label for="family" class="sr-only">選擇家族</label>
          <div class="select-field">
            <ChevronDown class="field-icon" aria-hidden="true" />
            <select id="family" aria-label="家族選單">
              <option value="all" selected>所有家族</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <h2>標籤</h2>
          <div class="tags"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-container fontPage-container"></div>

        <div class="header-links header-links-social">
          <a href="https://dc.elvismao.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Discord"><MessageCircle aria-hidden="true" /></a>
          <a href="https://github.com/emfont/emfont" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="GitHub"><Code2 aria-hidden="true" /></a>
          <a href="https://t.me/emfont" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Telegram"><Send aria-hidden="true" /></a>
          <label for="lightmode" class="lightmodeLabel" aria-label="切換色彩模式">
            <Moon class="theme-moon" aria-hidden="true" />
            <Sun class="theme-sun" aria-hidden="true" />
          </label>
          <div class="header-links header-links-font">
            <a href="https://github.com/emfont/emfont/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="意見回饋"><AlertTriangle aria-hidden="true" /></a>
            <a href="https://github.com/emfont/emfont/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="GitHub"><Code2 aria-hidden="true" /></a>
            <a href="/docs" aria-label="說明文件"><CircleHelp aria-hidden="true" /></a>
            <label for="lightmode" class="lightmodeLabel" aria-label="切換色彩模式">
              <Moon class="theme-moon" aria-hidden="true" />
              <Sun class="theme-sun" aria-hidden="true" />
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div id="bulletin" role="region" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true">
        <button id="closeBulletin" aria-label="關閉公告"><X aria-hidden="true" /></button>
        <p></p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <script src={`${apiBase}/emfont.js`}></script>
    <script>
      import "../scripts/site.ts";
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
